  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This award strives to advance freedom and dignity by assisting governments and citizens to establish, consolidate and protect democratic institutions, processes, and values, including participatory and accountable governance, rule of law, authentic political competition, civil society, human rights, and the free flow of information. More specifically, this includes Poleco Grant To Promote The Defense And Implementation Of The Gender Identity Law Within Public Institutions And Civil Society..</narrative>
